# Task 5 – Creation of Roles

## Project
Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description
This task focuses on creating custom user roles required for the Smart Library Request Workflow application. Two roles, **student** and **librarian**, are created to implement role-based access control.

## Steps Performed

1. Opened User Administration → Roles.
2. Created the **librarian** role.
3. Created the **student** role.
4. Verified that both roles were successfully added.

## Roles

- student
- librarian

## Expected Outcome

The application now supports role-based security, allowing different users to access only the features relevant to their responsibilities.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- User Administration
- Roles
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

## Status

Completed
